1 Dve bhojane, dure eva ca calante
2 ekayā dṛṣṭyā, pūrvam kṣudhāyā mriyate sma,
3 yaḥ svatantrataḥ puruṣaḥ ekam dantair bhakṣayet;

4 evam ekaḥ samvatsaraḥ sthāsyati dveṣayoḥ madhye
5 ugra-vṛkayoḥ, samam bibhyan;
6 evam ekaḥ śvā sthāsyati dveṣayoḥ madhye:

13 Abhavat tatra Beatricias tādṛśī yathā Danielaḥ,
14 Nabukodonosoram krodhāt pramādayan,
15 yaḥ krodhaḥ tam anṛtena kṛtvā nṛśaṃ cakāra;

31 na asti anyatra svarge teṣām āsanaṃ
32 etebhyaḥ ātmābhyaḥ ye adhunā te abhivyaktaḥ,
33 na ca asti teṣām sattve adhikaṃ vā alpam vā varṣāṇi;

43 Asmāt śāstram avatīrṇam
44 Yūyam yathā śaknuvanti tathā, pādayoḥ pāṇī ca
45 Parameśvarāya kalpayati, anyad eva abhipretya;

52 Aha ātmā svakīyāya nakṣatrāya punarāgacchati iti vadati,
53 tām tataḥ pṛthakbhūtām manyamānaḥ;
54 yadā prakṛtiḥ śarīram adadāt.

94 Ahaṃ tvām niścitaṃ manasi sthāpitavān asmi
95 yathā ātmā bhagavatī na śakyate mithyāvādinī bhavitum,
96 yataḥ sā nityam ādyasatyasya समीपे vartate;

97 atha ca tvam Piccardāt śrotum śaknoși
98 yathā āvaraṇasya sneham Konstaṃsā dhārayām āsa;
99 yathā sā atra mama saha virodham iva karoti.

100 Anekasmāt pūrvam, bhrātar, abhavat
101 yadi, bhayāt palāyitum, viparītam icchāyāḥ
102 tat kṛtam yena na kartavyam āsīt;

109 Niścitā kāmaḥ apradāyaṃ na anumanyate;
110 anumanyate tu tāvat, yāvat bibheti,
111 nivṛtte adhikaṃ kleśam āpatitum.

115 Evam āsīt taraṅgaḥ pavitra-nadyāḥ
116 yāḥ pravartate tasmāt mūlāt yasmad viśvam satyam pravartate;
117 evam ekaḥ eva ca anyaḥ ca icche śāntau nyavedayat.

121 mama snehaḥ naivam gambhīraḥ asti,
122 yena tvām anugraheṇa anugraham prati dātum śakyate;
123 api tu yaḥ paśyati sarvam ca karoti sa eva etasya prati-uttaram dadātu."
